    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offering a driver-focused E46 M3 featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six power plant. This unit benefits from a recently overhauled double VANOS system and a reinforced rear subframe to ensure structural integrity under lateral load. Power is delivered through a precise six-speed manual transmission and a factory M-Variable differential lock. The suspension geometry remains tight, utilizing refreshed bushings and OEM dampers for authentic road feel. This is a mechanically robust example, showing honest wear consistent with its age, but meticulously serviced to maintain its high-performance envelope.",
